00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:53,340
 and it's you see a create statement, right?

184
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:55,500
 And so this is the actual create statement

185
00:08:55,500 --> 00:09:00,500
 that the Django sent to sqlite to create the table.

186
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,740
 And I was talking about some of these things

187
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:03,660
 are quite predictable.

188
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:05,340
 The name of the column is quite predictable,

